data.persona: I make sure everyone stays under control. If someone starts making trouble, I am the one who gets to take care of it. I very much enjoy this type of work. I would only leave if someone could pay me more as a traveling bodyguard. That would be my idea of a great life!
data.description:
You are in the Cloud Nine Bar.
A bar in the clouds. Lively atmosphere with good drinks and even better views.
There's a dart board, some good drinks, and a jukebox here.
A bartender is here.

You are carrying a flask, a worn map, and a coin purse, wearing a leather jerkin, some leather boots, some pants, and a shirt, and wielding a dagger and a club.
